local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["hortative"]={"hortative","['hɔːtətɪv]","[ 'hɔ:tətiv ]","adj.激励的",'adj.激励的','A hortative sentence exhorts, advises and/or calls to action. An example would be "Ask not what your country can do for you, ask what you can do for your country."','激励性的语句用于劝告、建议和（或者）召唤行动。例如“不要问国家能为你做什么，而要问你能为国家做什么”。','The print is a hortative drawing. It tells us that everybody has shortcoming and the power of the individual is smaller than group.','这幅图片是一张勉励的漫画，他告诉我们每个人都有缺点，一个人的力量总是不如集体的力量的。'}
